```

Code

```verilog
package t_pkg;
  function void report_summarize();
    $display ("%m END!");
  endfunction : report_summarize

endpackage : t_pkg

module m;

  import t_pkg::*;

  initial begin
    $display ("%m From initial block");
    #10;
    $display ("%m ", $time);
    $finish(1);
  end

  final begin
    report_summarize();
    $display ("%m From final block");
  end
endmodule 


```

